{
  "stem": "4760.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he was always sick, one way or another, always sick with asthma.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he was a self-educated man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because of being so sick all the time, he had read and educated himself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he was a good friends with the-- what do you call it here?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like a deputy, deputy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Representative.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You would say that in French, a deputy, like a congressman, yes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a good friend with a congressman in Limoges.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this fellow heard that the German-- that the Germans were looking-- going to look for all the Jews in France, for all the Jews in the non-occupied France, because France was split.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was the occupied France and the non-occupied France.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we lived in the non-occupied France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So France was-- so he heard about that the Germans were going to look for all the German Jews in the non-occupied-- Territory.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Territory, in Limoges, in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jews from France didn't have to worry about the German Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he called him in the afternoon and told my uncle, make sure your sister and husband and the children get out of your house and see what you can do and hide them, if you can.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that afternoon, I went over to-- to those nice farmers and explained to them my situation, what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That we had just a phone call from a friend of ours in Limoges that they were going to look for all the Jewish children and some Jewish families, more than that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if they could take me for awhile over to stay with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Naturally, you know, it's-- it's difficult, but they agreed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I went to their cousin who-- and-- and explained it to their cousin, [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jean. ?] He was in the Maquis.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
